聆听 The Libertines 喧闹的新单曲“Oh Shit” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-libertines-rowdy-new-single-oh-shit-3597419?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-the-libertines-rowdy-新单曲哦该死Liberty DunworthWed, 06 Mar 2024 09:43:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3597419 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="浪荡子，2024。" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它标志着新专辑“All Quiet On The Eastern Esplanade”中的最新单曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-libertines-rowdy-new-single-oh-shit-3597419">Listen to The Libertines 的喧闹新单曲“Oh Shit”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="浪荡子，2024。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Libertines@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">The Libertines</a>分享了一首喧闹的新单曲，名为“Oh Shit”——请在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-interview-pete-doherty-carl-barat-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-3517826">The Libertines 谈论干净和联系：“我们只是想在当下写出优美的歌曲”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这首单曲于今天（3 月 6 日）发行，是独立老将即将发行的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/libertines-run-run-run-new-album-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-margate-tour-3514134">《All Quiet On The Eastern Esplanade》</a>中的最新单曲——继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/libertines-run-run-run-new-album-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-margate-tour-3514134">《Run, Run, Run》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-libertines-new-single-night-of-the-hunter-3554310">《Night Of The Hunter》</a>之后和 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-libertines-dramatic-new-song-shiver-3573574">“颤抖”</a> 。</p><p>这首歌由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carl-barat">Carl Barat</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">Pete Doherty</a>创作，从头到尾都是 The Libertines 的典型，成员们创作了一首耳虫赞歌，为日益困难的时期注入了急需的能量。</p><p>这首歌是为现场演奏而制作的，以欢快、高能量的吉他连复段开始，然后主唱以“ <em>Imo 喜欢在阳光下滚动的感觉/在海洋中滚动/她滚动直到麻木</em>”开场。</p><p> “<em>她走了/哦该死，哦该死/让我们赚点钱/刚好够我们过日子，</em> ”他在国歌副歌中唱道。 “<em>当你微笑时我想要你/你的眼睛里充满了美元。</em> ” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="妈的" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ebUWPhIhnxg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The Libertines 定于 4 月 5 日发行，他们于 10 月份首次宣布了他们的新专辑的消息，该专辑是酝酿已久的 2015 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-libertines-new-album-anthems-for-doomed-youth-track-by-track-first-listen-review-16186">《Anthems For Doomed Youth》</a>的后续专辑，并放弃了主打单曲《Run, Run, Run》。 。 <a href="https://thelibertines.tmstor.es/?lf=9e8bf8e83972416a00d7a4cdfa53b2da" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-interview-pete-doherty-carl-barat-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-3517826">乐队当时还接受了<em>NME</em>采访</a>，并回忆了他们是否认为自己是注定要成为的乐队。</p><p> “我认为我们并不真正知道我们想成为什么样的乐队；我们只想在那一刻写出优美的歌曲。恰巧此时此刻，我们都面向同一个方向。”巴拉特说道。</p><p> “大家都非常关注，每个人都在努力寻找自己在世界上的位置。每个人的生活都有很大不同，我们设法找到一些可以团结起来的东西。这就是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-hotel-albion-rooms-margate-carl-barat-video-tour-interview-2770049">The Albion Rooms</a>真正擅长的地方——以实体形式提供，并且由每个人共同拥有。感觉就像是这个已经持续了一段时间的旅程的一部分。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="浪荡子乐队在《东方滨海艺术中心一切安静》中谈论清洁和联系" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CtuPJQWz_mQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>除了分享唱片的消息外，独立巨头还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-announce-autumn-uk-and-ireland-2024-tour-buy-tickets-3588644">宣布了一系列将于秋季开始的英国和爱尔兰巡演日期</a>。</p><p>这些演出将于 9 月 23 日在都柏林 3Olympia 剧院上演，并于第二天在贝尔法斯特继续演出。</p><p>从那时起，其余的主要巡演日期将在十月和十一月举行，包括在卡迪夫、布里斯托尔、格拉斯哥、伦敦、纽卡斯尔等城市的演出。他们将在曼彻斯特阿尔伯特音乐厅连续三个晚上（11 月 7 日、8 日和 9 日）结束本次比赛。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-libertines-tickets%2Fartist%2F945319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>购买旅游日期的剩余门票。</p><p>在巡演日期之前，The Libertines 还将开展一系列店内表演以庆祝专辑发行，并于 7 月 28 日（星期日）在布莱顿<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-announce-huge-summer-2024-show-at-brighton-beach-buy-tickets-3584417">举行“海滩音乐节”。</a> <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-libertines-tickets%2Fartist%2F945319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>了解更多信息并查找门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-libertines-rowdy-new-single-oh-shit-3597419">Listen to The Libertines 的喧闹新单曲“Oh Shit”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
