英国独立唱片店数量创10年来新高https://www.nme.com/news/music/number-of-uk-independent-record-shops-hits-10-year-high-3597354?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=number-of-uk-independent-唱片店销量创十年新高Hollie GeraghtyWed, 06 Mar 2024 08:58:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsVinyl https://www.nme.com/?p=3597354 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="独立唱片店 Reckless Records" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>相比之下，自 2014 年以来实体销售音乐的商店数量有所下降</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/number-of-uk-independent-record-shops-hits-10-year-high-3597354">英国独立唱片店数量创 10 年来新高的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="独立唱片店 Reckless Records" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/uk-record-shop-high-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据最新的行业调查结果，英国独立唱片店的数量已创 10 年来新高。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2024-full-list-releases-vinyl-3588062">2024 年唱片店日：查看完整发行列表</a></strong></li></ul><p>数字娱乐和零售协会 (ERA) 表示，英国现在有 461 家独立唱片店，比 10 年前增加了 122 家（来自<em><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/newsbeat-68483084" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC</a></em> ）。</p><p> <a href="https://www.eraltd.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ERA 的 2024 年年鉴</a>（今天 3 月 6 日出版）包含音乐、视频和游戏领域的统计数据，还发现去年英国音乐市场价值 22 亿英镑。其中 84% 归因于流媒体订阅。</p><p>然而，实体销售音乐的商店（如超市和专业连锁店）的数量在此期间从 10,391 家减少到 2,486 家。</p><p>与此同时，黑胶唱片的需求连续第 16 年持续增长。售出 650 万辆，总销售额超过 1.7 亿英镑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3597396" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3597396" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3597396" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/record-store-day-2019.jpg" alt="人们参加伦敦一年一度的唱片店日活动" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/record-store-day-2019.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/record-store-day-2019-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/record-store-day-2019-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/record-store-day-2019-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/record-store-day-2019-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/record-store-day-2019-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3597396" class="wp-caption-text">人们于 2019 年 4 月 13 日在伦敦参加一年一度的唱片店日活动。唱片店日是一项于 2008 年启动的年度活动，于每年 4 月的一个星期六举行，旨在庆祝独立拥有的唱片店文化。这一天聚集了世界各地的歌迷、艺术家和数千家独立唱片店（图片来源：Alberto Pezzali/NurPhoto via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>据报道，其中 220 万张唱片是通过独立商店出售的。其他调查结果包括总销售额中的 1.1 亿英镑是由旧版本产生的。</p><p>首席执行官金·贝利 (Kim Bayley) 在一份声明中表示：“尽管独立公司主要由所有者兼经理经营，但他们已经摆脱了来自该国一些规模最大、资金最雄厚的公司的竞争。</p><p> “独立游戏已经找到了自己的定位，并且将继续留在这里。</p><p> “这表明，尽管音乐流媒体取得了压倒性的成功，但许多音乐迷仍然致力于高街实体音乐购买体验。”</p><p>该调查结果是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-vinyl-sales-2023-reach-highest-level-since-1990-3563676">英国黑胶唱片销量于 2023 年达到 1990 年以来的最高水平之后得出的</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">1989（泰勒版）</a> 》是当年最畅销的专辑，其次是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队的</a>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-rolling-stones-hackney-diamonds-review-lyrics-tracklist-3515754">哈克尼钻石</a>》。</p><p>与此同时，在美国， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-in-every-15-vinyl-records-sold-in-us-in-2023-was-by-taylor-swift-3572169">2023 年售出的每 15 张黑胶唱片中就有一张是 Swift 的</a>。</p><p>今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2024-full-list-releases-vinyl-3588062">唱片店日将于 4 月 20 日星期六在英国各地举行</a>，让歌迷有机会购买来自数百位艺术家的特别的一次性收藏版黑胶唱片、卡带等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daft-punk">Daft Punk</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">Lily Allen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gorillaz">Gorillaz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">Elton John</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">Noel Gallagher 的 High Flying Birds</a>等艺术家均参与其中。您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2024-full-list-releases-vinyl-3588062">在此处查看完整的版本列表</a>。</p><p>本周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-byrne-to-cover-paramores-hard-times-for-record-store-day-2024-3597053">大卫·伯恩 (David Byrne) 还宣布，他将在 2024 年唱片店日翻唱帕拉莫尔 (Paramore) 的《Hard Times》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/number-of-uk-independent-record-shops-hits-10-year-high-3597354">英国独立唱片店数量创 10 年来新高的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
